commit.message:
actions.h: Standarize copyright statement.

        * actions.h: Standarize copyright statement.
        * except.c inout.c lang.c lex.c lex.h loop.c nloop.c: Likewise.
        * parse.c tasking.c tasking.h timing.c xtypeck.c: Likewise.
